<span id="freeTextContainer18095039074133315290">I do not think I like Amanda Quick&apos;s heroes either. They&apos;re all so cool. Marble. Ice men. Emotionless. They NEVER give anything away to their heroines. Can&apos;t crack a smile, much less a joke. This irks me. Badly.<br/><br/>And if I have to hear the words: Metaphysical, transcendental, or higher plane one more time....there will be explosive projectile vomiting. <br/><br/>The ending was the best part. It&apos;s over now.<br/><br/>3 stars is a high rating. But I suppose it is apt.</span>
