<div id="review_432246086" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/432246086" />
    <a title="Mo" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13030645-mo"><img alt="Mo" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1366636609p2/13030645.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/432246086?book_show_action=true">Oct 11, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mo" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mo" href="/user/show/13030645-mo">Mo</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13030645-mo?shelf=bodice-ripper">bodice-ripper</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13030645-mo?shelf=brit-lit">brit-lit</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13030645-mo?shelf=2015">2015</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13030645-mo?shelf=owned">owned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13030645-mo?shelf=read-more-than-once">read-more-than-once</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer432246086" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11720704989102109099">I first read this novel in 1991, which is almost 25 years ago. I&apos;ve since read it about 5 times.<br/><br/>Funny, I used to love the character of Emily. This time around I found her naiveté to be rather tiresome. And if I had to read the word &quot;metaphysical&quot; one more time, I was going to scream!<br/><br/>I&apos;m going to let the 5 star rating stand, but I guess I am past this book now (or I&apos;m really tired of it). It was more of a 3 star this time around.</span>
  <span id="freeText11720704989102109099" style="display:none">I first read this novel in 1991, which is almost 25 years ago. I've since read it about 5 times.<br /><br />Funny, I used to love the character of Emily. This time around I found her naiveté to be rather tiresome. And if I had to read the word "metaphysical" one more time, I was going to scream!<br /><br />I'm going to let the 5 star rating stand, but I guess I am past this book now (or I'm really tired of it). It was more of a 3 star this time around.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11720704989102109099" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review432246086">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link432246086" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=432246086&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F367749.Scandal">flag</a>





