<span id="freeTextContainer3618729787065013546">This is still one of my all-time favorite books. It&apos;s hilarious, sexy, and has some action thrown in. A bit bonkers, but in a fun way. Be aware there is some problematic fetishism of &quot;the East&quot;, and CW for suicide of a family member in hero&apos;s backstory.<br/>The audiobook narration was way over-the-top, so I&apos;d recommend reading from an ebook or paperback.</span>
  <span id="freeText3618729787065013546" style="display:none">This is still one of my all-time favorite books. It's hilarious, sexy, and has some action thrown in. A bit bonkers, but in a fun way. Be aware there is some problematic fetishism of "the East", and CW for suicide of a family member in hero's backstory.<br />The audiobook narration was way over-the-top, so I'd recommend reading from an ebook or paperback.</span>
